{
  "texts": [
    "The annotators were asked to rate individual evidence based on relatedness to the claim and their utility in fact checking.",
    "To evaluate the QuanTemp dataset, we introduce a baseline factchecking pipeline.",
    "We fix the retriever model (BM25 + re-ranking) for all experiments.",
    "After extensive experiments, we choose to finetune the Roberta-Large-MNLI 3 model, pre-fine-tuned on the MNLI corpus, for the NLI task.",
    "In Section 4.4 we further explore various NLI models' effectiveness on numerical claims."
  ]
}